"applications that can be installed. On some devices, this may mean making"
" sure the box marked next to *Unknown Sources* is not checked or to "
"uncheck it, if needed. On other devices, there may be a different way to "
"turn off *Unknown Sources*."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/features/features.rst:408
msgid "*Settings > Security > Phone Administration > Unknown Sources*"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/features/features.rst:410
msgid "**Turn on App Verification**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/features/features.rst:412
msgid ""
